{
  "stem": "6924.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally, we spotted the box with the-- with the money and the jewels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There wasn't a big fortune there, but I would estimate it according with our-- with our-- according to dollars, maybe it was worth between 4-- or $5,000.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The thing was-- was from $20-- gold and $20, with a few-- some jewelry there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, anyway, after he took that back out, I was very nervous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know what's gonna-- But he walked with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went back to the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went to his house, put everything on the table, and we started to dividing things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He saw one thing, it was a golden watch, Dina's father's watch, a golden watch with a chain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said he liked that-- to have that watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took that watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And right away, he gave me, for that, for the watch, he gave me three 20-- golden $20 pieces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was more than the worth of the watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we divided evenly-- even.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he took me back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I already felt a little bit better, because at work, the next day, he treated me-- you know, he was-- I felt a little bit better that-- he treated me like-- like somebody special, not just like an average.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got in touch with Dina, and I said, first thing, try to get me out from that Lackie.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Try to get me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Try to get me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some-- there was always communication there, because some people who worked in Lackie went to-- to the town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was where she was working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] was in town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was communication by writing, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
